%8B%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%2520%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%B9%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E9%9A%8A%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%3Fmtc%3Db0008&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0e5745b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2239420/【特朗普洩密】上載訪伊拉克照片%20美軍海豹突擊隊成員曝光?mtc=b0008</a>"},{"pid":"f6c9ace8b745156e73db8935d9d7be6a8d5a727c","tid":959151,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"班飛虎都有肥佬 唔出奇<br />\n睇得戲多以為個個都馬德鐘同Anthony Mackie<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ae13664d1072917eb7dd393df26a21c95abaa7","tid":959151,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"On9侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bfdfb0da6ad42039ad415d84c21029b3f23941","tid":959151,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"01342b8e9babc32d823b9f9232d8d50f14b77f7f","tid":959151,"uid":150320,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"41c0f831435291a0ff99e32fca7dbe1623b8507d","tid":959151,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普日前閃電訪問伊拉克後，又鬧出洩密風波。特朗普在社交平台上載探望美軍片段和與戰士合照，但影象並未打格，令美軍海豹突擊隊成員樣貌，以及部隊最新部署曝光。情報專家質疑，特朗普此舉可能危害美軍行動安全。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周三聖誕節訪問伊拉克後，在社交平台Twitter上載探望美軍影片。片段長1分23秒，紀錄了特朗普與美軍合照、開會等情景，美軍成員樣貌、制服上標誌等細節清晰可見。<br />\n<br />\n《新聞周刊》（Newsweek）報道指，部分與特朗普合照戰士，相信是美國海軍海豹突擊隊第五分隊（SEAL Team 5）成員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2235000/2239420/782817-01-02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2235000%2F2239420%2F782817-01-02_1024.jpg&h=617d5e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲ 特朗普與海豹突擊隊成員Kyu Lee合照<br />\n分隊牧師Kyu Lee向特朗普報上軍銜後，特朗普稱︰「既然如此，我們一起合照吧。」（''Hey， in that case， let's take a picture''）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2235000/2239420/783374-01-02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2235000%2F2239420%2F783374-01-02_1024.jpg&h=0fccaa7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2235000/2239420/782898-01-02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2235000%2F2239420%2F782898-01-02_1024.jpg&h=bf391e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報道引述國防部官員稱，特朗普有責任保護特種部隊成員的身份，美國官方則慣常在照片和影片中，為敏感信息，包括特種部隊人員面孔打碼。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍前情報專家南斯（Malcolm Nance）稱，片段令部署在戰區的特種部隊成員身份曝光，惟特種部隊成員的真實姓名、樣貌和身份都是機密，如果他們被敵對政府拘留或被恐怖組織挾持，揭露他們身份等於為對方宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 鄧燕君<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2239420/%E3%80%90%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E8%A8%AA%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%20%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%B9%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E9%9A%8A%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89?mtc=b0008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2239420%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E5%25AF%2586%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BC%2589%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%2520%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25B1%25B9%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%2593%258A%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%3Fmtc%3Db0008&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f267bcd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2239420/%E3%80%90%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E8%A8%AA%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%20%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%B9%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E9%9A%8A%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89?mtc=b0008</a><br />\n<br />\n個個人好似香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"東方昇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"國家級任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6d47234aa70f834502574f6967997bdec2c881","tid":959151,"uid":155732,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d5ec1872d419b2c9655e1359f39a78029bc2cf74","tid":959151,"uid":11148,"like":48,"dislike":3,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"NAVY 巴打 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"Go_Navy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b985f8dfc2dcab68a86a587382b02575eaf6b8","tid":959151,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f277c97b431c30433a6893a4668f5d10803fb860","tid":959151,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"戴眼鏡都做得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"後勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc3f2eafd0b1668add1335392ce19c5b563d1b0","tid":959151,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e8ddada3206bbe10eea9a85211c9ae0799ddc6","tid":959151,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"海軍少校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"Go_navy巴黎好似講過係校級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219a9c59840d33da5aa8470f0bdccc6c773ac0d6","tid":959151,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海軍少校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Go_navy巴打好似講過係校級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}